description-of-drawings.p: FIG. 1 is a perspective view illustrating a computing device according to our new design;
FIG. 2 is a front view thereof;
FIG. 3 is a back view thereof;
FIG. 4 is a side view thereof;
FIG. 5 is another side view thereof;
FIG. 6 is a top plan view thereof; and,
FIG. 7 is a bottom plan view thereof.

The broken lines in the drawings illustrate portions of the computing device that form no part of the claimed design. The unshaded regions bounded by broken lines in the drawings illustrate the bounds of the claim and form no part thereof. Non-oblique line shading represents contour and not surface ornamentation.

claim.claim-text: The ornamental design for a computing device, as shown and described.
